name: Roaming Adventurer
info: Experienced adventurers exploring in space. Average capacity\ has a lot of wonderful equipment. \ Originally has 100 energy.
condition: Unlock the game for the first time

name: Space thief
info: Organizations that regularly rob other spacecraft in space. The lucky value is very high\has props that increase money. At the beginning there were 1,000 gold coins.
condition: Accumulated 99999 gold coins to unlock in the game

name: Star Alliance Members
info: The core members of the current galaxy alliance \ in order to find the wreckage of the organization \ to find the truth of the matter and go forward \ good at high speed weapons.

name: Loners
info: Lonely man wanders alone in space. Only 2 aircraft can be controlled but the spacecraft attack power can be greatly enhanced.
condition: Clear any mode 10 times to unlock

name: Robot
info: Robots with autonomous thinking ability have very good control over the spacecraft. The chip you are carrying allows you to clearly observe the state of the enemy.
condition: Accumulated 9999 energy to unlock in the game

name: Mystery man
info: Unknown star traveler \ Always wears a hat \ No one knows his life experience (Special character \ Low ability bonus \ Unequipped skills)
condition: Clear the normal mode to unlock

name: Time Traveler
info: For a purpose to cross the space-time \ come to this galaxy explorer \ \ At the beginning of the acquisition of several spacecraft and props.

name: Star Lord
info: Leading a galaxy leader\can increase the full capacity of the spacecraft.
